data.description: If you're looking for an open floor concept, great curb appeal, .45 acres, and an established neighborhood, then 401 Skyway Place could be the home for you! All four bedrooms are on the main level, with a stairway leading to bonus room over the garage. Bonus room has a separate closet and door that can serve as a 5th bedroom. This home sits in a prime location, being minutes from downtown Travelers Rest, State Park, convenient shopping, swamp rabbit trail, and much more!!
